//options screen Board Size: No. of minions: 3 * 4 4 * 6 8 * 12 6 10 15 20 Erase times played Skip Games played: Minions Remaining Moves Made: How To: \nSelect board size and the amount of minions you want to face in the options menu. To play the game, you have to get away from the minions by touching cells adjacent to yourself(stickman). If minions go into the same cell then it will kill both of them. Continue evading minions until your the last man standing! Or get killed by a minion occupying the same cell as you. http://www.cs.sfu.ca/~wsumner/teaching/276/15/
